Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise

Contains the controller implementation for the sunrise controller including it's IO interface.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFieldBusEventProvider
    Provides methods for adding or removing listeners on the Field bus.
    IJointTorqueSensorReferenceState
    Provides information about the referencing state of the joint torque sensors (JTS) for a joint device.
    IPositionReferenceState
    Provides information about the referencing state of the position sensors for a joint device.
    ISSRExecutor
    Interface for sending SSRs to Sunrise real time system.
    ISSRFuture
    Future reflecting execution of one SSR.
    IStatePortListener
    Notification interface for controller state port events.
    IStatePortProvider
    Provides access to states ports of a controller.
    ISunriseConnection
    Connection to Sunrise real time system implementing SunriseAPI interface.
    ISunriseRobot
    A robot controlled by Sunrise.
    ISunriseSensorModuleConnection
    Interface to configure and monitor a sunrise sensor module.
    ISunriseTools
    Capability interface containing some low level Sunrise functions.

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    LbrTemperatureBusData.JointTemperatureSensor
    This enumeration contains communication information about sensor data on bus for joint related sensors (motor/JTS (joint torque sensor) temperatures).

    This enumeration contains communication information about sensor data on the bus for the temperature sensors on the PDS board.

Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise Description

Contains the controller implementation for the sunrise controller including it's IO interface.
This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
